This paper is about image co-segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses deep learning-based methods, which falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG) subcategories. Additionally, the paper discusses object cues and correlation cues, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR) subcategories.
